{"tid":640121,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[興趣班]有沒人試過係香港西廚學院上西餐烹飪班","createTime":"2018-04-24T04:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T17:54:44.000Z","uid":81211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fd77fdd6d146abfe819cd57fd0307b64108c0a86","tid":640121,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身都有睇開奶閪Bob同Gordon Ramsay，但最近想有系統學下點煮西餐，聽聞工聯會質素又好麻麻，跟住就搵到依間野<br />\n<br />\nCourses: Starter &amp; Main<br />\nStudent can learn to make starter and main course, most of them are popular in european countries. Student can enjoy the meals and rise up the styles of diet.<br />\n<br />\n1. Cream of Carrot, Different Cuts<br />\n2. Casear Salad, Chicken Consomme<br />\n3. Asparagus with Hollandaise Sauce, Coq au vin<br />\n4. Fish Stock, Panfried fish fillet (sole, Meuniere), Cooking of Sole Grenobloise<br />\n5. Shrimp Cocktail, Cooking of potatoes, Croquette Potato, Roast Spring Chicken<br />\n6. Home made pasta / dry pasta / ravioli - pasta sauce<br />\n7. Egg Mayonnaise, Roast pork (butt), roast potato, gravy<br />\n8. Kjotsupa Iceland Lamb Soup, Roast Rack of Lamb<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://culinary.com.hk/index/courses/professional-interest-short-courses/general-cookery/starter-main-course-beginner?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fculinary.com.hk%2Findex%2Fcourses%2Fprofessional-interest-short-courses%2Fgeneral-cookery%2Fstarter-main-course-beginner%3Flang%3Den&d=vHuKfvF7bamx%2B%2BckcQho88PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2d0a69f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://culinary.com.hk/index/courses/professional-interest-short-courses/general-cookery/starter-main-course-beginner?lang=en</a><br />\n<br />\n睇落都好似正正常常，有沒巴打試過係到上堂？或者有其他介紹"},{"pid":"b83d135d82236c43ff6639ae8c6a78fcebc79387","tid":640121,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac